# Rust build output
/target

# Tauri-generated native projects (regenerated by `tauri android/ios init`).
# The shell, config, and Rust backend are the source of truth; the Xcode /
# Gradle projects are generated artifacts.
/gen

# This package only carries the Tauri CLI; deps install on demand.
/node_modules

# Desktop-set byproduct of the `tauri icon` stamp in patch-xcode-project.sh;
# only the gen/apple asset catalog it also writes is what the build uses.
/icons
